data.description: Rare opportunity for an Owner-Occupant or Investor.  Live in one side and rent the other! Two-story side has 3 bedrooms and 1.5 baths, and partially finished basement. One-story side has 2 bedrooms and 1 bath with basement. Both sides have fenced yards and one-car garages. Updates include - Windows (2019), Roof (2023), Furnaces (2024), Water Heaters (2022). Mix of updates and original finishes, well-maintained. Tenant Occupied - Curb Offers. LIMITED VIEWING OPPORTUNITY on 2/22 - CONTACT YOUR BUYER'S AGENT.
